<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Judoscale Test Application</h1>

  <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Load Testing Tools</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Use these tools to test Judoscale autoscaling capabilities:</p>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 bg-gray-50">
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Slow Endpoint</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">This endpoint sleeps for a specified number of seconds before responding.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <a href="/load_test/slow?seconds=5" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">
            Test (5 seconds)
          </a>
          <a href="/load_test/slow?seconds=10" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">
            Test (10 seconds)
          </a>
          <a href="/load_test/slow?seconds=20" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">
            Test (20 seconds)
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 bg-gray-50">
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Concurrent Slow Endpoint</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">This endpoint creates multiple threads that each sleep for a specified duration.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <a href="/load_test/concurrent_slow?threads=3&seconds=5" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">
            Test (3 threads, 5 seconds)
          </a>
          <a href="/load_test/concurrent_slow?threads=5&seconds=10" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">
            Test (5 threads, 10 seconds)
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Documentation</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">For more detailed information on testing Judoscale autoscaling, please refer to the <code>JUDOSCALE_TESTING.md</code> file in the project root.</p>

    <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Quick Commands</h3>
    <div class="bg-gray-800 text-white p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto">
      <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap">
# Run the load test script
bin/test_autoscaling.rb

# Run with custom parameters
bin/test_autoscaling.rb --concurrency 20 --requests 100 --sleep 15

# Manual testing with curl
curl "http://localhost:3000/load_test/slow?seconds=10"
curl "http://localhost:3000/load_test/concurrent_slow?threads=5&seconds=10"
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
